OL,7,FFormer Liverpool women's team manager
OL,8,FMatt Beard has died aged 47, the club
OL,9,Fhave announced.
OL,11,FBeard had two spells as manager of the
OL,12,FReds and most recently left the
OL,13,FWomen's Super League club in February
OL,14,Fthis year.
